---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import ProjectCta from '../components/ProjectCta.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Gold Concentrator"
  description="An ore-led mineral processing team combining more than ten years of core experience with gravity testing, flowsheet design and equipment delivery."
>
  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'About' }]} />
      <span class="eyebrow">Independent process integration</span>
      <h1>About Gold Concentrator</h1>
      <p>
        Gold Concentrator is built around a simple operating principle: understand the ore and
        process duty before selecting the equipment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-shell">
      <article class="prose">
        <h2>Experience belongs to the team, not an invented company history</h2>
        <p>
          Our core team brings more than ten years of mineral processing experience. We describe
          that experience accurately and do not present it as the age of the Gold Concentrator
          brand.
        </p>
        <h2>Focused on practical gravity concentration</h2>
        <p>
          Gold is the primary market and the reason for the domain. The underlying capability also
          applies to tin, tungsten, chrome and other minerals where density difference, liberation
          and particle size support gravity separation.
        </p>
        <h2>Clear limits build better projects</h2>
        <p>
          Our stable test capability focuses on gravity response. We coordinate other specialist
          programs where needed. We publish project performance only when evidence and operating
          conditions support it.
        </p>
      </article>
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <span class="eyebrow">Contact details</span>
        <h2>Launch information required</h2>
        <p>
          Add the real office or contracting address, professional mailbox, WhatsApp number and
          company registration details before public deployment.
        </p>
        <a class="button" href="/assess-my-project/">Discuss a project</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
  <ProjectCta />
</BaseLayout>
